ratification vote ultimately he joined the 935 majority which 
ratified the treaty 
last month when the democraticcontrolled congress was deciding 
whether to approve a pentagon budget quayle said reagan should 
veto the bill because it cut too deeply into the star wars budget 
it was advice reagan followed even though more moderate 
republicans such as sen john warner rva said reagan should 
