bill quayle moved to have it returned to a housesenate conference 
committee to increase the star wars budget and strip out 
democraticwritten arms control restrictions 
this is a political struggle between the administration and 
the congress over who is going to run arms control policy no 
question about it quayle explained 
quayles move lost 5835 and he was one of the first 
legislators to praise reagan when the president vetoed the bill 
aug 3 quayle termed the veto a good sound decision 
on the labor committee quayle and sen orrin hatch rutah 
have been the strongest administration supporters 
