the cost of arranging the soviet withdrawal from afghanistan and 
the ceasefire in the iraniraq war will leave the united nations 
financially strapped 
the tab for peacekeeping missions will increase from roughly 25 
percent of the un budget to more than twice the entire budget in 
fact the un could run out of funds by november 
peace may be breaking out all over but no one is breaking out 
his wallet 
one particularly important holdout is the united states which 
has been withholding its dues since 1985 charging that the 
organization was antiamerican 
now the united states is 467 million in arrears including this 
years assessment of 44 million 
