protracted patent fight over who invented the laser the company 
said 
the palo altobased company said tuesday it will pay tiny patlex 
corp of chatsworth calif license fees on the sale of most of 
coherents lasers 
the agreement leaves spectraphysics inc of san jose as the 
last major laser maker refusing to pay fees to patlex 
patlex is headed by former apollo astronaut and former eastern 
airlines chairman frank borman 
the agreement with patlex covers gas discharge lasers made by 
coherent and it protects coherents customers from patent 
infringement action by patlex 
patlex which would not disclose the terms of the agreement has 
asked for a 5 percent royalty from most laser makers 
coherent and spectraphysics are two of the worlds leading 
manufacturers of lasers 
patlex is a small laser company that has a 64 percent interest 
in licensing income from patents it has secured over the years for 
inventor gordon gould gould came up with a design for a laser in 
